iterations.yara_rule:
rule Bypass_Sample
{
    meta:
        description = "Evasion bypass rule"
        cape_options = "bp0=$pattern0+0,action0=skip,bp1=$pattern1+0,action1=skip,bp2=$pattern2+0,action2=skip,count=0"

    strings:
        $pattern0 = { 52 56 57 50 FF D2 }  // Push edx/esi/edi/eax + call edx
        $pattern1 = { 56 56 E8 ?? ?? ?? ?? 85 C0 }  // Push esi x2 + call + test eax
        $pattern2 = { 56 56 50 51 FF D2 }  // Push esi x2 + push eax/ecx + call edx

    condition:
        any of them
}
